he\nantisites.\n  Hence they are not expected to occur in sufficient concentration to affect\nthe intrinsic Fermi level position. In particular, they do not contribute to\nthe unintentional n-type background doping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Aug 2017 16:04:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Oct 2017 17:01:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-01"}
